# Normalize all text files to LF in the working tree on every platform, so git's
# autocrlf never rewrites line endings on Windows checkout. churl's persistence
# saves LF, and the byte-identity round-trip tests compare a re-saved file
# against its `include_str!` fixture — a CRLF-converted fixture fails those on
# Windows even though the code is correct. Binary files are auto-detected and
# left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
